          .comment
            .comment__header
              .comment__header--author Константин Константинопольский
              .comment__header--rate(data-value="4")
                -for(i=1;i<=5;i++)
                  svg(xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg', viewBox='0 0 24 24'): polygon(points='12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2')
              .comment__header--date Jun 18, 2018
            .comment__body 
              | Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo. 
          .comment.last
            .comment__header
              .comment__header--author Константин Константинопольский
              .comment__header--rate(data-value="3")
                -for(i=1;i<=5;i++)
                  svg(xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg', viewBox='0 0 24 24'): polygon(points='12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2')
              .comment__header--date Jun 18, 2018
            .comment__body 
              | Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo. 
          .change__plan: span Удаление комментариев доступно в других пакетах. <a href="">Купить пакет</a>
      .create__controls
        .btn.blue(data-mfp-src="#public" data-mfp-type="inline")
          svg(xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"): path(d="M20.7 5.3a1 1 0 0 0-1.4 0L9 15.6l-4.3-4.3c-.4-.4-1-.4-1.4 0s-.4 1 0 1.4l5 5c.2.2.4.3.7.3s.5-.1.7-.3l11-11c.4-.4.4-1 0-1.4z")
          span Опубликовать
        .btn.blue
          svg(xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"): path(d="M21.7 7.3l-5-5a1 1 0 0 0-1.4 0l-13 13a1 1 0 0 0-.3.7v5c0 .6.4 1 1 1h5c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3l13-13c.4-.4.4-1 0-1.4zM7.6 20H4v-3.6l12-12L19.6 8l-12 12z")
          span Сохранить в черновик
        .btn.blue
          svg(xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24")
            path(d="M23.9 11.6C23.7 11.2 19.5 3 12 3S.3 11.2.1 11.6v.9C.3 12.8 4.5 21 12 21s11.7-8.2 11.9-8.6c.1-.2.1-.6 0-.8zM12 19c-5.4 0-8.9-5.4-9.9-7C3 10.4 6.6 5 12 5s8.9 5.4 9.9 7c-1 1.6-4.5 7-9.9 7z")
            path(d="M12 8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4 4 4 0 0 0 4 4 4 4 0 0 0 4-4 4 4 0 0 0-4-4zm0 6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2c0-1.1.9-2 2-2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2 2z")
          span Предпросмотр
        .btn.link(data-mfp-src="#cancel" data-mfp-type="inline")
          svg(xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"): path(d="M19 11H7.4l5.3-5.3c.4-.4.4-1 0-1.4s-1-.4-1.4 0l-7 7-.2.3c-.1.2-.1.5 0 .8l.2.3 7 7c.2.2.5.3.7.3s.5-.1.7-.3c.4-.4.4-1 0-1.4L7.4 13H19c.6 0 1-.4 1-1s-.4-1-1-1z")
          span Выйти
    #delete.mfp-hide.popup__default
      h3.popup__default--header Вы действительно хотите удалить комментарий? 
      .popup__default--body
        .btn.blue
          svg(xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"): path(d="M20.7 5.3a1 1 0 0 0-1.4 0L9 15.6l-4.3-4.3c-.4-.4-1-.4-1.4 0s-.4 1 0 1.4l5 5c.2.2.4.3.7.3s.5-.1.7-.3l11-11c.4-.4.4-1 0-1.4z")
          span Удалить
        .btn.cancel(data-mfp-close)
          svg(xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-x")
            line(x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18")
            line(x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18")
          span Отмена
